graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Operator<br/>v0.7.0]

    %% External Dependencies
    Kueue -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.22+]
    Kueue -->|TLS certificates| CertManager[cert-manager or<br/>internal-cert]
    Kueue -->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus Operator]
    Kueue -->|node provisioning| Autoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler<br/>autoscaling.x-k8s.io]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    Kueue -->|queue ML training jobs| KubeflowTraining[Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>TFJob, PyTorchJob, MPIJob]
    Kueue -->|queue Ray workloads| RayOp[Ray Operator<br/>RayJob, RayCluster]
    Kueue -.->|monitoring integration| PromIntegration[Prometheus<br/>PodMonitor, PrometheusRule]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|potential UI integration| Kueue
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|batch job orchestration| Kueue
    Notebooks[Notebooks/Workbenches] -.->|submit training jobs| Kueue

    %% Workload Types
    Jobs[Kubernetes Jobs<br/>batch/v1] -->|managed by| Kueue
    JobSets[JobSet<br/>jobset.x-k8s.io] -->|managed by| Kueue
    KubeflowTraining -->|creates| MLJobs[TFJob, PyTorchJob,<br/>MPIJob, XGBoostJob]
    MLJobs -->|intercepted by| Kueue
    RayOp -->|creates| RayWorkloads[RayJob, RayCluster]
    RayWorkloads -->|intercepted by| Kueue

    %% Core Kubernetes Resources
    K8s -->|provides API for| CRDs[Kueue CRDs<br/>ClusterQueue, LocalQueue,<br/>Workload, ResourceFlavor]
    Kueue -->|watches/creates| CRDs

